data.prayer: Spirit, make the Word of God a delight to the people of Aileu, like it was to David.
data.verse: I delight in your decrees; I will not neglect your Word.

data.location_label: Photo from the state of Aileu, Timor-Leste

data.prayer: Lord, please give the 4,550 believers in the state of Aileu the Spirit of wisdom and revelation, so that they might know you better.
data.verse: I keep asking that the God of our Lord Jesus Christ, the glorious Father, may give you the Spirit of wisdom and revelation, so that you may know him better.

data.prayer: Lord, help the people of Aileu, Timor-Leste to discover the essence of being a disciple, making disciples, and how to plant churches that multiply.
Lord, the the state of Aileu will disappear one day, but your Word will never disappear. Call all who claim Christianity to anchor their lives on your Word.
data.verse: Heaven and earth will disappear, but my words will never disappear.

data.prayer: Jesus, defend your people in the state of Aileu against the difficulty of these last days.
data.verse: But mark this: There will be terrible times in the last days. 2 People will be lovers of themselves, lovers of money, boastful, proud, abusive, disobedient to their parents, ungrateful, unholy, 3 without love, unforgiving, slanderous, without self-control, brutal, not lovers of the good, 4 treacherous, rash, conceited, lovers of pleasure rather than lovers of God— 5 having a form of godliness but denying its power.

data.prayer: Spirit, supernaturally prepare encounters with the gospel on sites like Facebook and Instagram for the 45,500 people living in Aileu.

data.section_summary:
the state of Aileu, Timor-Leste has a population of 45,500.

We estimate Aileu has 4,550 people who might know Jesus, 40,040 people who might know about Jesus culturally, and 910 people who do not know Jesus.

This is 1 believer for every 9 neighbors who need Jesus.

data.prayer: Jesus, all authority was given to you, and you commanded all disciples in Aileu, Timor-Leste to make more disciples, and you promised to be with them. May your power and their obedience make more disciples today.
data.verse: All authority in heaven and on earth has been given to me. Therefore go and make disciples of all nations, baptizing them in the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit, and teaching them to obey everything I have commanded you. And surely I am with you always, to the very end of the age.
